 {"id":"bd-v5fqf","title":"Task: Implement context pack caching layer","description":"Cache context packs to reduce redundant generation.\n\n## Implementation\n```go\n// internal/ensemble/context_cache.go\ntype ContextCache struct {\n    CacheDir string  // ~/.cache/ntm/context-packs/\n    TTL      time.Duration\n}\n\nfunc NewContextCache() *ContextCache\nfunc (c *ContextCache) Get(projectRoot string) (*ContextPack, bool)\nfunc (c *ContextCache) Set(projectRoot string, pack *ContextPack) error\nfunc (c *ContextCache) Invalidate(projectRoot string) error\nfunc (c *ContextCache) InvalidateAll() error\n\n// Cache key computation\nfunc (c *ContextCache) computeKey(root string) string\nfunc (c *ContextCache) isStale(pack *ContextPack) bool\n```\n\n## Invalidation Triggers\n- Code changes (git status dirty)\n- New commits since generation\n- TTL expiry (default 1 hour)\n- User explicit request (--no-cache)\n\n## Storage Format\n```\n~/.cache/ntm/context-packs/\n  {project-hash}.json  # Serialized ContextPack\n  {project-hash}.meta  # Metadata (generated_at, git_sha)\n```\n\n## File: internal/ensemble/context_cache.go","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-23T08:00:55.098873713Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-23T09:16:16.001053571Z","closed_at":"2026-01-23T09:16:16.001010780Z","close_reason":"Duplicate of bd-15yvf","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-v5fqf","depends_on_id":"bd-2ouwm","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-23T08:00:55.129838536Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-v5fqf","depends_on_id":"bd-dkxa0","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-23T08:09:54.757309606Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
